        <num>CC 2051</num>
        <heading>2051.  Contract worded in general terms</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2051.  Contract worded in general terms
Although a contract is worded in general terms, it must be interpreted to cover only those things it appears the parties intended to include.</p>
        </content>
